      "title": "Notification of the Ministry of External Affairs",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "All consular offices of the Ministry of External Affairs have been decided to remain open on all weekdays.",
        "The Ministry of External Affairs has announced that this will be implemented from July 4.",
        "In addition, the Ministry of External Affairs has announced that the Regional Offices of Jaffna, Matara, Kandy, Kurunegala and Trincomalee will also be operational. (a)"
      ],
